points, lines, bars, or even violin plots"}),", choosing the right geom is key to effectively communicating your data story."]})]})},{name:"stats",module:[1],description:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)("p",{children:[(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"Statistical layers"})," focus on the transformation of the data before it's plotted, making complex computations easier."]}),(0,t.jsxs)("p",{children:["While geoms define the visual representation, stats handle statistical transformations—useful for e.g."," ",(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"adding labels to bars and computing group-wise summaries"})," ","without manual preprocessing."]})]})},{name:"scales",module:[1,2],description:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)("p",{children:[(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"Scales"})," control how mapped data values are visually represented and how they appear in your plot."]}),(0,t.jsxs)("p",{children:["They allow you to ",(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"customize axes and legends"})," by adjusting breaks, labels, and limits, refine ",(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"shape encodings"}),", or override default ",(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"color palettes"})," to improve clarity and storytelling."]})]})},{name:"coordinate system",module:[1,5],description:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)("p",{children:["The ",(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"coordinate system"})," determines how data is positioned, and sometimes a simple switch can transform how your plot is perceived."]}),(0,t.jsxs)("p",{children:["While ",(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"Cartesian coordinates"})," are the default, alternatives like"," ",(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"polar coordinates"})," open up creative possibilities for visualizing circular data. Coordinate systems also play a major role when creating maps: proper projections ensure that"," ",(0,t.jsx)("b",{children:"geographic data"})," is accurately represented."]})]})},{name:"spatial data",module:[5],description:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)("p",{children:[(0,t.jsx)("b",{child